## WPML

- Queries often pass `'lang' => apply_filters('wpml_current_language', null)`.
- PG/MBA permalink filters and city-in-URL rules live at bottom of `cpt-taxonomy.php`.
- News bases: PL `aktualnosci`, EN `news`, UK `novyny`, RU `novosti` (`ata_news_base_by_lang()` in `configure.php`).
